%% Admin Upload Flow - Mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant AdminBrowser
  participant Frontend
  participant Backend
  participant Cloudinary
  participant DB

  AdminBrowser->>Frontend: open Product Image Upload
  Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/admin/products/upload (file)
  Backend->>Cloudinary: upload file
  Cloudinary-->>Backend: returns URL
  Backend->>DB: save product record with image URL
  Backend-->>Frontend: product saved
